{"tid":2330482,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"(face id 末日）出賣自己的臉作面具 賣得好還可以分紅！","createTime":"2020-12-18T05:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T08:53:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c8d6e1f03ae1726bfeee0bb4214600c7fb771ffb","tid":2330482,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:11:35.000Z","msg":"日本人的創意真的讓人意想不到，最近在日本又出現一件讓人討論度極高的商品，就是「3D打印人臉面具」。<br />\n來自東京的「特製口罩」商Kamenya Omoto，最近公開了一款名為「That Face」的「3D打印人臉面具」，只要當時人願意，他們會出4萬日圓（約港幣2,983元）來買下其他人臉的版權，來製作面具。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BBgBRBN8PrCNX0Cc88LUYA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-12/10b82140-35fe-11eb-bfec-c182c6765eb5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBBgBRBN8PrCNX0Cc88LUYA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi42NjY2NjY2NjY2NjY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-12%2F10b82140-35fe-11eb-bfec-c182c6765eb5&h=a16867ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一轉手他們以約7萬8千日圓（約港幣5,817元）出售你樣子的面具，如果你的臉特別受歡迎，你更可以按比例分到花紅！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過出售自己樣子的做法爭議很大，雖然有不少人反對，不過卻有很多對整個計劃感到興趣，原本只限定東京地區的人可以賣自己的臉，現在更，開始考慮要透過抽籤來選擇日本其他地區的臉孔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKamenya Omoto表示，不允許被選中的人透露自己的身分，而製造商也保證不會外流你的肖像或是個人訊息。不知道又是否可以用在iPhone上的Face ID呢？"},{"pid":"ea3352e92278dc48c71199103f918ae4c4c73a00","tid":2330482,"uid":8304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:13:49.000Z","msg":"只值三千<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33e964abbffbcc5c24bc7ce87d5e766939ac666","tid":2330482,"uid":171786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"正，可以真正做到蒙頭入閘"},{"pid":"bfe2dde49f647d7c7ec9748a980ce1529db51b7a","tid":2330482,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"想買"}